{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_10_01",
  "title": "鈴村優 1話 優が大変お世話になってます",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、優\n今、少し時間をもらってもいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ Yu.\nCan I have a moment of your time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\nもちろんええで。お仕事のことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ good work.\nOf course. Is it about work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、優に新しく広告動画のオファーがきたんだ\n家族旅行の魅力を伝える、ドラマ仕立ての動画らしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ you have received a new offer for an advertising video.\nIt's apparently a drama-style video promoting the appeal of family trips.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "先日の舞台で優の演技を観て\nぜひ優に出演をと、先方が強く希望しているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After seeing Yu's acting in the recent stage play‚\nthey strongly want you to appear in it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ……よぉ分かってはるなぁ～\nうちの新たな魅力に、早速魅せられてもうたんやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu… they really get it~\nThey've already been captivated by my new charm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（確かにいい演技だったが、苦労したって聞いてるぞ）\n（……なんて突っ込むのは、さすがに野暮だな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Her acting was certainly good‚ but I heard she struggled.）\n（…but pointing that out would be tactless.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.8666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "……？　{user}さん\n何か言いたそうな顔してませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…? {user}-san‚\nyou look like you want to say something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あぁ、いや……そうだな……\nそういえば二点、気がかりなことがあるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-ah‚ no… well…\nSpeaking of which‚ there are two things I'm concerned about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "例の舞台の円盤特典の撮影と、今回の仕事の時期が\n重なっていてな。無理がないよう気をつけたいのと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The filming for the bonus features of that stage play's disc overlaps with this job‚\nso I want you to make sure not to push yourself too hard…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それから……今回の広告動画なんだが\n鈴村久美子さんと優の、親子共演を組みたいそうなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also… for this advertising video‚\nthey want Kumiko Suzumura-san and Yu to co-star as parent and child.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　うちのママ……やなくて、お母さんと？\nそれって……お母さんはもう受けたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? With my mama… I mean‚ my mother?\nDoes that mean… has my mother already accepted?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2333285013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "久美子さんは「娘との共演なんて嬉しい、喜んで」\nと快諾したらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kumiko-san said \"I'm happy to co-star with my daughter‚ gladly\"\nand readily agreed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7333285013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "うちも嬉しい！　お母さんと共演出来るなんて\n舞台を頑張らへんかったら、一生なかったことや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm happy too! Co-starring with my mother…\nIf I hadn't worked hard on the stage‚ this never would have happened.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2333285013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、うちも喜んでやらせてもらいます\n予定が詰まってても、こんなん挑戦するしかありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I'll gladly do it too.\nEven if my schedule is packed‚ I have to take on this challenge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.5666618346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "役者としてのお母さんに演技の稽古をつけてもらって\n同じプロとして、さらに尊敬するようになったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having my mother‚ an actress‚ coach me in acting‚\nI've come to respect her even more as a fellow professional.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.599993642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "人を魅せる仕事の大先輩として\nお母さんとの共演は、学ぶところが多いと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a senior in the business of captivating people‚\nI think there's a lot to learn from co-starring with my mother.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.899993642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "そういう意味でも楽しみやし\nあの舞台を観てのオファーというのも嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m really looking forward to it for that reason‚\nand I’m glad the offer came as a result of that stage play.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.9999926248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "きっと人気俳優、鈴村久美子の娘やから\n与えられた機会なんは分かってるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know I’m probably being given this opportunity because\nI'm the daughter of the popular actress Kumiko Suzumura‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.2999926248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "親の七光りやって言われても\nそういう声は実力で黙らせてみせます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but even if people say it's riding on my mother's coattails‚\nI'll prove them wrong with my own ability.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.9666592914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……優の気持ちはよく分かった\n先方には、すぐに返事をしておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… I understand Yu's feelings well.\nI'll give them an answer right away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.1999926248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "親子共演と聞いて、なおさらやる気満々です\nうち、頑張りますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hearing about the parent-child collaboration makes me even more motivated.\nI'll do my best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.3666582742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。ただ俺は、お母さんっていうきっかけはあっても\nこれは優が自分自身の実力で得た仕事だと思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. But even though your mother was the catalyst‚\nI think this is a job you earned with your own ability.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.4333249408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "だから――親の七光りだなんて、誰にも言わせない\n俺が優を守るから、安心して撮影に臨んでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I won't let anyone say it's riding on your parent's coattails.\nI'll protect you‚ so please approach the filming with confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.0999905902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nありがとうございます、ほんま安心やわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nThank you‚ I'm really relieved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.4333239236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "……ただ、うーん……ちょっと引っかかるなぁ……\n言っても仕方ないことやって分かってるんやけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But‚ hmm… something's bothering me…\nI know it's pointless to say though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.9666572569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ？　何かあるなら言ってくれ\n不安なことは事前に解消しておいた方がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is it? If there's something‚ please tell me.\nIt's better to resolve concerns beforehand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.8999905902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "ほんなら言うけど、こないに力強く「俺が守る」なんて\n言われて、うち、ついドキッとしてもうたんやけどな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ I'll just say it‚ being told \"I'll protect you\" so strongly\nmade my heart skip a beat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.8666572569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "こうもさらっと甘い言葉が出てくるやなんて\n他の子にも粉かけて惑わせてるんちゃうかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saying such sweet things so smoothly‚\naren't you flirting with other girls too‚ making them fall for you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.9666572569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "こ、粉？　待て待て、そんなことしてないからな？\nそもそも今のはマネージャーとして守るって意味で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ch-charming? Wait wait‚ I'm not doing anything like that!\nTo begin with‚ I meant protecting you as a manager…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.7666572569,
      "sfxList": []
